<plot>A loose Flemish TV comedy format in which Gaston Berghmans, the surviving member of the popular Antwerp (dialect!) stand-up comedians duo with Leo Martin (which toured the theaters of Flanders as well as making occasional TV programs and even a few movies), presented and starred in most of the short, widely varied comical sketches, without much further structure, rather just consecutive jokes.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?210585</url></doc>
